name: FedEx 757-236SF [N959FD] Landing and Close Up Taxi at Edmonton Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
This spot is the closest you can get to the action at Edmonton International Airport, and it's always fantastic when anything big like a 757 takes this taxiway. Here we have Edmonton's weekday flight from FedEx arriving from Memphis just after sunrise on Runway 02 back in May. ATC is included, as it often is, hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
